title: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? classSet is not expected class
description: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? The output is "MySomeClass".
OB: When invoking ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) method, the output is "MySomeClass".
EB: The expected output is not "MySomeClass". The classSet should contain the expected classes.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Invoke the ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet) method.
2. Check the output and observe that it is "MySomeClass" instead of the expected classes.
